Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(308,397)}漫迪字幕组倾情奉献\N\N——·旗木译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mack 写一下"男生就是这个星球苦难的源泉"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mack, make that "boys are the scourge of the Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}男生不许在课堂上嚼口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,《泄密的心》? 我超爱言情小说\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Telltale Heart? I love romance novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}神秘及幻想故事集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 没什么比暗恋中的砰然之心更能表达"我要你"了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, nothing says "be mine" like a pounding heart beneath a floorboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,注意了 年轻人们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Attention, young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我要宣布个激动人心的消息\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have an exciting announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,格鲁夫希尔 专收天赋异禀及优秀学生的学校\N{\fnArial\fs18}Grove Hills, the school for gifted and outstanding students,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已向我校发出邀请 请我们的几位同学过去参观\N{\fnArial\fs18}has issued invitations to several of our students to visit its campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这几位有幸的同学分别是:\N{\fnArial\fs18}And among those so honored are:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer同学和Landon同学\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Morgendorffer and Ms. Landon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道数学一路得了及格是福不是祸\N{\fnArial\fs18}I knew those straight Cs in math would pay off some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,破盘子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Damn plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 妈妈跟我说格鲁夫希尔访问的事了 有你的 小鬼\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, mom told me about Grove Hills. That's great, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦待在一个所有孩子都觉得他们比我酷的学校了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm tired of being at a school where the kids just think they're cooler than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去一个他们也觉得自己比我聪明的学校\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to go to one where they think they're smarter than me also.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 太为你骄傲了 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I'm so proud of you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,格鲁夫希尔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Grove Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里认识的朋友会切实有助于你的前途\N{\fnArial\fs18}The friends you make there could really launch your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,周末应该上网 干嘛要去上学?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And why study when you can network?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是去参观下 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's just a visit, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当初他们也是这么跟肯尼迪说的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what they told J.F.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,给你20块钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll pay you $20.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一百\N{\fnArial\fs18}A hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你怎么从来都不贿赂我?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! How come you never offer me a bribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们俩是一伙儿的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because we work together as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搞定这死丫头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fnArial\fs18}Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,给你20块钱 我来搞定行吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I give you $20 will you let me handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一百\N{\fnArial\fs18}A hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 四十 - 六十\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Forty. - Sixty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 五十 - 成交\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Fifty. - Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 五十? - 成交\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Fifty? - Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这周末去格鲁夫希尔中学\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to Grove Hills this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们圈养那些学霸怪咖的地方吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}That place where they fence in all the geeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛我也得去啊? 讲不讲理啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why do I have to go? That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 恐怕姐妹什么的没被邀请呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, I'm afraid siblings aren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你就留在家里\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're staying home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说全家人都出去玩只留下我?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean the whole family gets to go without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,讲不讲理啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 你们不在的时候我会好好照看家里的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't worry, I'll take good care of the house while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说像上次那样 在家里开小酒桶派对\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean like last time, when you had that keg party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeffy还在老妈的橱柜里吐了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}and Jeffy threw up in Mom's closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人家才没 是Jerome\N{\fnArial\fs18}He did not. It was Jerome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁 我还是不太倾向让你一人在家\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't like the idea of you staying here alone, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么? 我又不害怕\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why? I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你有毛可害怕的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. Why should you be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怕大屠杀凶手 连环杀手 虐待狂 食人族...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of mass murderers, serial killers, torturers, cannibals...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,虐狗狂?\N{\fnArial\fs18}puppy kickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈\N{\fnArial\fs18}Muh-om!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你去Sandi家吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe you can stay at Sandi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我豁出去给那个Linda巫婆打个电话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Even if I have to call that witch, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda? 还好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Linda? How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚达成了今年目标业绩的120%\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I just made 120% of my target projection for this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了红利和一张激励支票\N{\fnArial\fs18}earning me a bonus and an incentive check,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以特么好爆了 你呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}so I'm pretty damn good. How you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我今年过得也蛮好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I'm having a good year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对 今年蛮好 没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, a very good year. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太谢谢你让Quinn这周末去你家了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, thank you so much for letting Quinn stay with you this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 这孩子偶尔需要家长监督下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, she sometimes needs a little supervision...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我有严格的基本家法\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't worry. I've got firm ground rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,第一点也是最重要的 男孩免进\N{\fnArial\fs18}First and foremost: no boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对免进\N{\fnArial\fs18}N-O, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandi会用棍子把他们都打跑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sandi has to beat them off with a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在开什么玩笑?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我在她这个年纪也总惦记臭小子\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had the same problem at her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ricky和其他男生会在塔尖街等着咱们\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Ricky and the guys will be waiting for us at Tower Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抹防污口红\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wear smudge-proof lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经把车钥匙藏起来了 以防她有二心\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've already hidden the keys to the car, in case Sandi gets any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,话说我以前也拿棍子打过他们来着\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, I used to have to beat them off with a stick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就又配了一把车钥匙了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I made a copy of the keys to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上围巾 以免发型乱了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Bring scarf to avoid convertible hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,十一点必须熄灯\N{\fnArial\fs18}And lights out by 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说没? 我也拿棍子打跑过男孩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you hear that? About the stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等十一点我妈查完房以后\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then, after my mother checks on us at 11:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就从窗户跑出去 开上车 去见那帮男生\N{\fnArial\fs18}we climb out my window, grab the car, and meet the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 Sandi 你想的真是万无一失\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boy, Sandi, you've thought of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得你是时尚俱乐部的主席呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No wonder you're president of the Fashion Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 Linda 你想的真是万无一失\N{\fnArial\fs18}My, Linda, you've thought of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得你能加入朗岱尔女企业家联盟呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No wonder you're on the board of the Lawndale Businesswoman's Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢载我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸妈会在他们俱乐部的新成员早午餐会后来找我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}My parents will meet us up there after the new members' brunch at their club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸盼着入会都盼了三年了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My father's been on the waiting list for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 不管一路上发生了什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}Remember, no matter what happens on this ride
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你已放弃"因某些人神经质对你造成束缚"而起诉我的权利\N{\fnArial\fs18}you've already waived your right to sue me for confining you with lunatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,话说Jodie 你有在哪个俱乐部吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Jodie, do you belong to any clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以选择不回应\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't have to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我是法语俱乐部的主席\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm president of the French Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,学生会副主席 年鉴编辑\N{\fnArial\fs18}vice president of Student Council, editor of yearbook,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还在校网球队\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I'm also on the tennis team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你怎么没在校网球队啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, why aren't you on the tennis team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为其被归类为运动\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because it's classified as a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来运动了 Jodie 你认识Kevin Thompson吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Speaking of sports, Jodie, do you know Kevin Thompson?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他和Daria一起做过科学实验来着\N{\fnArial\fs18}He and Daria did a science project together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,认识的 Kevin很棒的...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sure. Kevin's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,擅长往自己脑袋里泼啤酒罐\N{\fnArial\fs18}at smashing beer cans with his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我真搞不懂为什么Daria不肯和他还有他朋友们多玩玩\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know why Daria doesn't hang around with him and his gang more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和我睡觉不把脑袋塞进冰里是一个理由\N{\fnArial\fs18}For the same reason I don't sleep with my head packed in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,话说Jodie 有男朋友没?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Jodie, got a fella?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有的 他叫Michael\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, his name's Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过大伙都叫他Mack\N{\fnArial\fs18}But everyone calls him Mack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去主楼吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Should we go to the main building,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还是去马棚申请临时工就行了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}or just apply for jobs in the stables?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就跟Peter说"听着...\N{\fnArial\fs18}So I told Peter, "Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不管你约过我多少次 你就不是我的菜"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't care how many times you ask me out. You're not my type!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,了解 我都记不清他约过我多少次了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know. I don't know how many times he's asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这话我刚说的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你刚说的是你才不管他约过你多少次\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, you said you don't care how many times he's asked you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是说...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, look, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿的凉鞋和你的同款\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's wearing sandals like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是重播么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this a rerun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不是 我去给你拿听健怡怎样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think so. Can I get you a diet soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 谢谢 不过你可以喝点葡萄汁\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, thanks. But help yourself to the grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,据说葡萄汁对皮疹有帮助\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hear they're good for breakouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 姐 你看啥呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, sis, what you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,换回来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Turn it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩小东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}You little geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么不看《时尚视野》了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, what happened to Fashion Vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sorry, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃花生酱卷糖吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, you want a peanut butter log?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要换更好的杯子吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Need a smoother glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮你解鞋带吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Should I fluff your shoelaces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩要是这么喜欢Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you guys like Quinn so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以考虑收养她 然后我去和Morgendorffer一家生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}maybe you should adopt her and I can go live with the Morgendorffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赞 - 我去给你打包\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Cool. - I'll help you pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 这儿变得有点挤了呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, it's getting kind of crowded in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiffany家应该宽敞些\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe Tiffany has more room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这话什么意思 Sandi?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you mean, Sandi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}遇见新希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好 欢迎来到格鲁夫希尔 我是Marina\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello, welcome to Grove Hills. I'm Marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Jodie\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm Jodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodie Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jodie, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我介绍Lara Graham和Cassidy\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd like you to meet Lara, Graham and Cassidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还好吗? - 很高兴认识你们\N{\fnArial\fs18}- What's up? - Hi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lara 不如你给Jodie和Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Lara, why don't you fill Jodie and Daria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,介绍下格鲁夫希尔式教育的诸多优势吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}in on the many advantages of a Grove Hills education?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 优势一:\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需在这种冒牌聚会上才需要招徕声尖调高的招生员\N{\fnArial\fs18}you only have to put up with shrill recruiters at phony functions like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿你不会像在家里一样...\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you're not surrounded by nearly as many stupid people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被那么多笨蛋包围\N{\fnArial\fs18}as you would be at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就比如说你爸妈吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Starting with your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,或许这地方没那么烂呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe this place isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来格鲁夫希尔 你可以在宽敞的宿舍里冥思蒲鲁斯特\N{\fnArial\fs18}At Grove Hills, you can contemplate Proust in our spacious dorm rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}法国化学家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在美味的一饭之间与同学用拉丁语交谈\N{\fnArial\fs18}engage in conversation in Latin over a delicious meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们风景优美的钟楼上一跃跳河\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dump bodies into the river from our scenic bell tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要犹豫 就是格鲁夫希尔 你的智慧之旅第一站\N{\fnArial\fs18}So all aboard to Grove Hills, your first station on the track to wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希望大伙都喜欢我们的小短片\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope everyone enjoyed our little film.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到一个很棒的开启本次欢迎会的方式\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think a super way to start this meet and greet session
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来分享一下各自的人生目标\N{\fnArial\fs18}would be to tell a little about our goals in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁愿意开个头呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who'd like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望有一天能拥有自己的公司\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, someday I'd like to own my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是个面向初创公司的咨询所吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe a consulting firm geared toward minority start-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 Daria 你的目标是什么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excellent! Daria? What about your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我没有诶...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, come, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你起码会有一个目标的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You must have some goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的目标就是不要在40岁醒来时 痛苦地意识到\N{\fnArial\fs18}My goal is not to wake up at 40 with the bitter realization
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一个恨之不及的岗位上浪费了一生\N{\fnArial\fs18}that I've wasted my life in a job I hate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我在年少时被迫决定自己的事业方向\N{\fnArial\fs18}because I was forced to decide on a career in my teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到格鲁夫希尔这座神圣殿堂\N{\fnArial\fs18}Welcome to the hallowed halls of Grove Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,诸位是否认为\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think it's a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,富人与权贵之人相识只是巧合之事呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}that the rich and powerful all seem to know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再想想吧 他们在学校便已结识\N{\fnArial\fs18}Think again. They met at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别让您天赋异禀的子女沦落在公立学校的洪流中\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't let your gifted progeny drown in the public school system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说开来\N{\fnArial\fs18}After all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,您是希望他们更早地得到长春藤联盟的垂青?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Would you rather they get an early acceptance to the Ivy League,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还是停滞在三流大学的水平呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}or stagnate at some third-rate college?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 咱们母校诶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! The old alma mater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,二位就是Jodie父母吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}You must be Jodie's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为何这么说?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在下Andrew Landon 我爱人Michele\N{\fnArial\fs18}Andrew Landon. My wife, Michele.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Andrew\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Andrew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,刚看你把豹牌汽车停那边了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Saw you parking your Jag out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,送给自己的小礼物 庆祝成功抬高了摞层咖啡杯的装水量\N{\fnArial\fs18}A little gift I bought myself after hitting the big figures with my folding coffee cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要义在于一定不要让层与层之间的缝隙漏水\N{\fnArial\fs18}The key was finding a way to keep the damn creases from leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 我曾经想到发明吸力助动的指甲剪呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, I came up with the idea for the suction-powered nail clipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可谁料到被一哥们儿先发制人了\N{\fnArial\fs18}But then somebody beat me to the punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我小儿子Evan 中后卫的料 有没有?\N{\fnArial\fs18}My boy, Evan. A linebacker, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说我不爱闺女 但Evan 他让我后继有人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that I don't love my girls, but Evan, he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodie跟我们说你的事了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jodie told us all about you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为了要孩子 宁可放弃在美利坚世界的副主席高位\N{\fnArial\fs18}walking away from a senior vice presidency at U.S. World to have a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是勇气可嘉 很多女人...\N{\fnArial\fs18}That took guts. A lot of women...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 Evan确实是意外怀的\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, so Evan wasn't planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不在乎\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没准我能劝动Helen再要个儿子呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe I could talk Helen into having a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没准我能劝动你离婚时把房分给我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe I could talk you into letting me keep the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这张照片会不会显得我鼻子跟嘴靠太近了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Does this picture make my nose look too close to my mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没 它俩之间的距离蛮舒服的\N{\fnArial\fs18}No. They're a comfortable distance apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我的牙呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about my teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,门牙有点太白了 对不对?\N{\fnArial\fs18}The front ones aren't too white, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没 它们的洁白程度再合适不过了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, they have just the right amount of whiteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能去卡仕曼购物中心了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can we go to Cashman's now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这身让我看起来胖吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Does this make me look fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这身让我看起来胖吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Does this make me look fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fnArial\fs18}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这身让我看起来胖吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Does this make me look fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你特么压根不胖 好嘛?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're not freaking fat, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我都说不完多喜欢Jodie了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I can't tell you how much I like Jodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望Daria和她人缘一样好\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just wish Daria were as popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,既然Jodie交朋友都那么上手 Daria又怎会不行?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, if Jodie can make friends so easily, why can't Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodie交朋友为什么要不上手呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why should Jodie have any problems making friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,朗岱尔高中的少数民族学生比较少嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, there's not a lot of... diversity at Lawndale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一小拨孩子的思想是很狭隘的 不会轻易接受...\N{\fnArial\fs18}A few people can be narrow-minded and not always accept
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来自不同社会背景的"突如其来"的孩子\N{\fnArial\fs18}"right away" people from different backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodie的社会背景跟Daria又有什么不同?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How is Jodie's background any different from Daria's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪下 我去趟洗手间\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me while I... use the ladies room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,知道什么会惹毛我吗 Jake兄?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know what riles me, Jake-o?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的福利骗局\N{\fnArial\fs18}Those damn welfare cheats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我没...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地可以伪造帐目\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank God for creative accounting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我得花一半的家底养活那些好吃懒做的工人\N{\fnArial\fs18}or I'd be spending half my net supporting those couch potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 但...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,全都因为假惺惺地禁止美国公司再雇佣童工\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because of those lousy cheats that American companies end up using child labor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 该死的福利骗局\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah... damn welfare cheats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,许多兢兢业业的美国人偶尔还是需要一些帮助的\N{\fnArial\fs18}A lot of hard-working people just need a little help now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,福利政策没啥可吐槽的 对吧 Michele?\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's nothing wrong with that, right, Michele?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得我会支持福利政策?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What makes you think I'm in favor of welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴你来我家玩的 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm so glad you're staying here, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别和任何人说哦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't tell anybody this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,时尚俱乐部的人里面 我最喜欢你了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but I like you best out of everyone in the Fashion Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这话真贴心 Stacy\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, that's nice, Stacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 看Bridgett穿的吊带裙\N{\fnArial\fs18}God! Look at Bridgett in that slip dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吊带裙?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Slip dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,其实吧 我想说你是我最好的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}In fact, I'd say you're my first-best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiffany是我第二好的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}And Tiffany's my second-best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandi是第三好的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sandi's my third-best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候Tiffany会变成第三 Sandi变成第二\N{\fnArial\fs18}Although sometimes Tiffany's third and Sandi's second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但你永远是最好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you're always first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 随便啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你最喜欢谁呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, who do you like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy 人家在读这篇打理睫毛的文章呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stacy! I'm trying to read this article on eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对 抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, right, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信她居然穿这种东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ugh! I can't believe she's wearing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,吊带裙太过时了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Slip dresses are so over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 吊带裙太过时了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, slip dresses are so over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,话说Quinn 要不要去看电影?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Quinn, want to go to a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 你想看什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure. What do you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 你想看什么就看什么咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know, whatever you want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿了一身什么呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我穿什么呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you want me to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那又是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以做一个相同颜色的渐变染\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought we could color our hair the same shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我先走了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都说高中应该是人生中最快乐的时光\N{\fnArial\fs18}They say high school's supposed to be the happiest time of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你的人生足够短\N{\fnArial\fs18}Only if your life is extremely short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太对了 你很幽默\N{\fnArial\fs18}Exactly. You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给别人一次机会 大家是可以做朋友的吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}See what happens when you give people a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最快乐的时光应该是赚到第一个一百万\N{\fnArial\fs18}Our happiest years will begin when we make our first million.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真等不及一手搂一个大妞儿漫步在里维埃拉\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't wait to stroll down the Riviera with a model on each arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}南欧沿地中海一地区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 那会有意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gee, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你虽然天赋异禀 但也可以道德败坏\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess you can be intellectually gifted and still be morally bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我求之不得呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I certainly hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信David还敢来这儿招摇\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't believe David has the nerve to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为他是谁啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了? 考试作弊了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What did he do? Cheat on a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,更甚 我们今天拿到了能力测验成绩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Worse. We got our S.A.T. scores back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,David只排到了90%的位次 白痴\N{\fnArial\fs18}David's were only in the 90th percentile. Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是没法跟他继续玩耍了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just can't hang out with him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他太... 平庸了\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's too... banal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,过去他这个人非常有趣的\N{\fnArial\fs18}And he used to be so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢标准化测验的存在\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank God for standardized tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你永远不知道谁是自己的真朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}Otherwise you'd never know who your real friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我是说... 幽默\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right. I mean... amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,给别人一次机会 大家是可以做朋友的吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}See what happens when you give people a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria... 嘿大伙 等等\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria...! Hey, guys, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想借你电话用一下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I need to use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己的电话不能用吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's wrong with your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能用 我能借宿一宿吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nothing. Can I spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈说不许我一个人在家呆着\N{\fnArial\fs18}My mother says I can't stay home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证不告密 甚至会帮你开酒桶\N{\fnArial\fs18}I won't say a word. I'll even spring for the keg,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过剩下的打扫工作得你负责\N{\fnArial\fs18}but you have to pay for the dry cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才张罗派对 太晚了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's too last-minute to throw a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就煲一晚上电话粥呗\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then just talk on the phone all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,问你朋友 如果可以变成一瓶指甲油\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ask your friends, if they could be a nail polish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她们想变什么颜色 为什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}what color they would be and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦那套玩意了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sick of that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你得回家了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're afraid to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要\N{\fnArial\fs18}I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 没空床了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, no vacancies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 是我害怕啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, I'm afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,家里有超大狗狗连环杀手什么的\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's mass serial puppy killers and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 求你还不行嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证会后悔的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意 我已经后悔了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Never mind, I already do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在格鲁夫希尔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Here at Grove Hills,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坚信 家长的参与至关重要\N{\fnArial\fs18}we strongly believe that parental involvement is imperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是非常赞同\N{\fnArial\fs18}I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,作为格鲁夫希尔家长 诸位需要参加每月董事会议\N{\fnArial\fs18}As a Grove Hills parent, you'll be attending monthly board meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,周末大扫除派对 筹款启动会\N{\fnArial\fs18}weekend cleanup parties, fund-raising drives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,您在核计?\N{\fnArial\fs18}do you collate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定会来 如果有时间 不过时间不多\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, I would if I had the time, which isn't often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力到场 日程允许的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll try to be here, schedule permitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我比较关心 到底多少学生最后能上重点大学?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was wondering, just how many students go on to top colleges?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,91%\N{\fnArial\fs18}91 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那剩余的这9%的学生要去向何处?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what kind of schools do the other nine percent go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有些学生在完成格鲁夫希尔的学业后 需要休息\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, some students require a bit of... rest after Grove Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休息什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What kind of rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,各位懂的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有时逃脱分数压力需要休息\N{\fnArial\fs18}some time away from the pressure of grades
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,逃脱竞争压力也需要休息\N{\fnArial\fs18}and away from the pressure of competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再有些时候 逃脱装扮压力挑食压力也需要休息\N{\fnArial\fs18}and occasionally away from the pressure of dressing and feeding themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在来这儿之前 我是个流浪天才\N{\fnArial\fs18}Before I came here I was an intellectual outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,会因为引用Ayn Rand的话被嘲笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}They made fun of me for quoting Ayn Rand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}俄裔美国哲学家 小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为她令人烦倦的地方在于...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, I think she's pretty disturbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是重点\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是你知道她是谁\N{\fnArial\fs18}The point is that you know who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而在格鲁夫希尔 你可以和像我们这样的人讨论她\N{\fnArial\fs18}and that at Grove Hills, you can discuss her with people like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是一群废物白痴 或者什么四分卫\N{\fnArial\fs18}instead of idiots and fools and a quarterback
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在全学校里瞎嚷嚷你裹着毛巾洗澡\N{\fnArial\fs18}who tells the whole school you shower in a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我更愿见识写出有关毛泽东论文的四分卫\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd like to see a quarterback write a paper on Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得文化大革命...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think the Cultural Revolution is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一个还没踏进这所学校的人 你话未免太多了点吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have an awful lot to say for someone who doesn't even go to this school yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 为什么不先看看你能不能进格鲁夫希尔\N{\fnArial\fs18}It means why don't we see whether you get in to Grove Hills
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再开始听你扯长篇大论?\N{\fnArial\fs18}before we start listening to your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别因为某个运动员让你觉得自己像个衰货\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just because some jock made you feel like the loser you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就把怒气撒我身上\N{\fnArial\fs18}don't take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不是衰货 我智商165\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm not a loser! I have a 165 I.Q.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谁管你啊? 还不是一样的无聊悲催\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who cares? You're still boring and miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别一天到晚把脑袋当屁股用\N{\fnArial\fs18}Try taking your head out of your butt for once
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,睁开你那双小近视眼好好看看\N{\fnArial\fs18}and opening up your myopic little eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你165的智商是不是应该聪明到直接看出自己什么货色?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or doesn't your 165 I.Q. make you smart enough to see the way you really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证你这辈子别想再进这所学校\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll make sure you never set foot in this school again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,松了口气\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你要威胁我们呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}For a minute there I thought you were going to threaten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,认了吧 感觉爽爆了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Admit it. That felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有点啦 好吧 爽爆了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, a little. Okay, a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,挫Graham那样的混蛋可是生活的一大乐趣呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Busting on jerks like Graham is one of life's few pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该多挫挫才是\N{\fnArial\fs18}You should try it more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快别扯了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上手真快\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己一贯的消极作风是一种自卫 对吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You realize your negative approach to everything is self-defeating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 拿毒舌战胜别人感觉还不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, it's nice to know there's someone I can defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 挫了别人 你自己的痛苦可能减轻了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, you may spare yourself some pain by cutting everyone off,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但同时你也失去了很多好的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}but you miss out on a lot of good stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 Jodie\N{\fnArial\fs18}Look, Jodie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我太聪明太敏感了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm too smart and too sensitive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没法和这样一个世界 这样一个时代 这样一个我妹共处\N{\fnArial\fs18}to live in a world like ours at a time like this with a sister like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我确实错过了某些好东西 但这态度对我就是有效\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe I do miss out on stuff, but this attitude is what works for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就应该理解什么态度对我有效\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then you'll understand what works for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在家 我是Jodie\N{\fnArial\fs18}At home, I'm Jodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以随心所欲畅所欲言\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can say or do whatever feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但在学校 我是出众的黑人女同学\N{\fnArial\fs18}But at school, I'm the Queen of the Negroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是完美的非裔美国少年\N{\fnArial\fs18}The perfect African-American teen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是朗岱尔所有非裔美国少年的行为榜样\N{\fnArial\fs18}The role model for all of the other African-American teens at Lawndale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们别被我带坏呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oups! Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我更想像你一样生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}Believe me, I'd like to be more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我也得承认 有些时候我也希望自己能像你一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I have to admit, there are times when I'd like to be more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说某些时候\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm not saying all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那朗岱尔还是格鲁夫希尔?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Lawndale or Grove Hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是选朗岱尔吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sticking with Lawndale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来了这儿 我会被牛肉汉堡里的馅料毒死的\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I came here, I'd end up poisoning the sloppy joe mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你说得对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就能成为朗岱尔优秀学生代表了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm pushed to the breaking point being Miss Model Student at Lawndale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在这待一年非死不可\N{\fnArial\fs18}A year here might kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说他确实挺好挺萌的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, he was really nice and cute and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但他只比我高五公分诶\N{\fnArial\fs18}but he was only two inches taller than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可我所有的鞋子\N{\fnArial\fs18}and my entire shoe collection
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都只适合跟比我高七公分的男孩约会时穿\N{\fnArial\fs18}is based on the concept of dating guys three inches taller than me or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂抽象艺术\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't get abstract art.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会愿意看一群唧唧歪歪的六眼怪啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who wants to look at a bunch of squiggly six-eyed people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,人家在购物网上轻轻松松就能买到漂亮写实的猫咪油画\N{\fnArial\fs18}when you can get those really pretty cat paintings on the shopping network?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说我不想在艺术上浪费钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that I would ever waste money on art.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Janey 借点钱有吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Janey. You got any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,钱? 你要出去吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Money? Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意出去兜兜风哦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wouldn't mind going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 我不知道要不要和一个如此装扮的家伙出门\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course, I don't know if I'd want to go out with someone dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,记得Quinn吗? Daria她妹\N{\fnArial\fs18}You remember Quinn, Daria's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来了 Daria她妹 嘿\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah. Daria's sister. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我有名字好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me, I have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,知道 Daria她妹嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right. Daria's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是希望他能回来?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean you want him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他把你绑在椅子上\N{\fnArial\fs18}Even though he tied you to a chair
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,扔到车水马龙的八道高速路中间?\N{\fnArial\fs18}and left it on an eight-lane highway in the middle of rush hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时只是失心疯了\N{\fnArial\fs18}He got carried away by the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么能穿成这样就上电视?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How can she go on TV looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的确定不想去格鲁夫希尔中学嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So you're sure you don't want to go to Grove Hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛要去一个特殊学校学一无是处的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why go to a special school to learn useless information
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我在朗岱尔也能免费学\N{\fnArial\fs18}when I can do it at Lawndale for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是Daria 爸爸和我都觉得你这样是错过了一个重要的机遇\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, Daria, your father and I think you're passing up an important opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但你说...\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢 我们说过会尊重你的决定 我们必须信守承诺\N{\fnArial\fs18}However, we said we'd respect your decision, and a promise is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的? 那你答应给我买小马咯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? So I can have that pony now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你改变主意 随时可以告诉我们 好的吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you change your mind, sweetie, you just let us know, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便 你们觉得Landon一家怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, what did you think of the Landons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 特别好 - 没错 特好 特别好\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Very nice! - Yes, very nice, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们惹着人家了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You ticked them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没没没没\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然不一定非要去格鲁夫希尔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course you don't have to go to Grove Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会要求你做让你后悔的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd never ask you to do anything you'd regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh... me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你们觉得Morgendorffer一家怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what do you think of the Morgendorffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真是脑袋被门夹的一对\N{\fnArial\fs18}What a couple of head cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抵押贷款之家 亲爱的抵押贷款家\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mortgage, sweet mortgage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在想做点啥 亲爱的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you want to do now, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,临时分居?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Trial separation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就又说到别的事了\N{\fnArial\fs18}And then the other thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到底谁想到"块块手链"这蠢名字的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}who came up with the name "tennis bracelet" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来就像防汗带 要我说的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}It sounds like some kind of a sweatband, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,猜我会起什么名?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know what I'd name them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,腕饰\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wrist ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就像树木挂饰一样 只是放手腕\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's like a tree ornament, only for your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来很喜庆吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Doesn't that sound festive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快... 带她... 走\N{\fnArial\fs18}Take... her... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩怎么跑一块去的\N{\fnArial\fs18}This story I've gotta hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}我要写到手软
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,租个脑子吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Rent a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,《如何赢得友情以德服人》\N{\fnArial\fs18}How to Win Friends and Influence People.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,讲的都是好态度能为你赢得的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's about all the things a good attitude can get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这本也是讲态度的\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is about attitude as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}黑暗之心 (波兰裔英国作家约瑟夫·康拉德所著小说)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"年轻人深入未知疆域之旅\N{\fnArial\fs18}"A young man's journey into unknown territory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,和灵魂深处的野蛮暴行面对面"\N{\fnArial\fs18}brings him face-to-face with the savage brutality within his own soul."
